Enum CharacterType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<CharacterType>
      • client.entities.CharacterType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<CharacterType>

    public enum CharacterType
extends java.lang.Enum<CharacterType>
    Creates AtlasSprite animation arrays for each type of character. An AtlasSprite is like a Sprite but expects the format of a sprite in an atlas. Who'd have guessed?
    Author:
    Siavash
